 Didn't Do a Thing\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|11|3}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 19\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 19\n| Title               = A Hot Air Affair at the Fair\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|11|10}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 20\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 20\n| Title               = The Thing Goes to the Dogs\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|11|10}}\n| ShortSummary        = Ronald has entered his dog Countess in the Centerville Dog Show, but chaos ensues when Countess is dognapped by the troublesome Yancy Street Gang and it's up to The Thing to rescue her.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 21\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 21\n| Title               = The Thing Goes Camping\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|11|17}}\n| ShortSummary        = Benjy, his friends and Miss Twilly go on a camping trip as part of a special school project which is anything but relaxing with a bear running loose at their campsite and a big storm triggering a landslide that threatened the entire camp. \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 22\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 22\n| Title               = Dude Ranch Rodeo\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|11|17}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 23\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 23\n| Title               = Photo Finish\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|11|24}}\n| ShortSummary        = Benjy accompanies his friends to the Centerville Zoo which is sponsoring a photo contest and the Yancy Street Gang resorts to their usual dirty tactics to win.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 24\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 24\n| Title               = Lights, Action, Thing!\n