{"title_page": "2004 Kansas Democratic caucuses", "text_new": "{{Infobox election\n| election_name = 2004 Kansas Democratic presidential caucuses\n| country = Kansas\n| previous_election = 2000 Kansas Democratic caucuses\n| previous_year = 2000\n| next_election = 2008 Kansas Democratic caucuses\n| next_year = 2008\n| election_date = March 13, 2004\n| elected_members = [[2004 Alaska Democratic caucuses|AK]]\n| 3blank = {{abbr|RCDs|Regional caucus delegates}}\n| votes_for_election = 41 [[2004 Democratic National Convention|Democratic National Convention]] delegates (33 pledged, 8 unpledged)<br>The number of pledged delegates received is determined by the popular vote\n| candidate1 = '''[[John Kerry]]'''\n| image1 = [[File:John F. Kerry (cropped).jpg|160x160px]]\n| color1 = 00539f\n| home_state1 = [[Massachusetts]]\n| delegate_count1 = '''32'''\n| 3data1 = '''289'''\n| image2 = [[File:HowardDeanDNC-cropped.jpg|x160px]]\n| candidate2 = [[Howard Dean]]<br><small>(withdrawn)</small>\n| color2 = e7cf1e\n| type = presidential\n| ongoing = no\n| home_state2 = [[Vermont]]\n| delegate_count2 = 1\n| party_name = no\n| color4 = ff69b4\n| home_state4 = [[Ohio]]\n| delegate_count4 = 0\n| 3data4 = 41\n| image5 = [[File:John Edwards, official Senate photo portrait (cropped).jpg|160x160px]]\n| candidate5 = [[John Edwards]]<br><small>(withdrawn)</small>\n| color5 = e50100\n| 3data2 = 27\n| delegate_count5 = 0\n| home_state5 = [[North Carolina]]\n| map = \n| 3data5 = 35\n| outgoing_members = [[2004 Texas Democratic primary|TX]]\n| 4blank = Percentage\n| 4data1 = '''71.89%'''\n| 4data2 = 6.72%\n| 4data4 = 10.20%\n| image4 = [[File:Dennis Kucinich (cropped).jpg|x160px]]\n| candidate4 = [[Dennis Kucinich]]\n| 4data5 = 8.71%\n}}\n{{ElectionsKS}}The '''2004 Kansas Democratic presidential caucuses''' were held on March 13 in the U.S. state of [[Kentucky]] as one of the [[2004 Democratic Party presidential primaries|Democratic Party's statewide nomination contests]] ahead of the [[2004 United